Usage & Utilities              ....##............

    make depend
      will install any required perl module dependencies, assuming perl
      and App::cpanminus are installed. and make

    binpack
      makes some rectangular rooms, packs them together, and connects
      the whole lot with some doors. code may require tweaking

    circulator
      generates "circular" vaults of a given radius, to the extent not-
      square terminal fonts support that

        ./circulator 7

    spiralfoo
      spirals, or something akin. code will require tweaking
